title: Hawks Soar to Undefeated Soccer Season
text:
Hawks Soar to Undefeated Soccer Season 
By Norman Seawright III October 9, 2015 Updated Oct 9, 2015 at 10:47 PM CDT 
Hermantown, MN (NNCNOW.com) -- The Hermantown boys' soccer team completed an undefeated regular season by defeating the visiting Duluth Marshall Hilltoppers. 
The Hawks held Marshall scoreless while goals from Daniel Hedstrom, Siji Gonzalez (his 20th of the season), and Noah Hooey carried Hermantown to a 3-0 shutout.
